## Workflow Diagram

```
Start Work
    ↓
Identify project from context
    ↓
Read tasks.md → Find current task
    ↓
Read knowledge.md → Gather context
    ↓
Consult references.md → As needed
    ↓
Check repos/ exist → Clone if needed
    ↓
Implement / Analyze
    ↓
Update tasks.md → Mark complete
    ↓
Update knowledge.md → Record learnings
    ↓
Update references.md → Note quality
    ↓
Request confirmation → Next task
```

